{
  "stem": "6257.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then suddenly, there was a kind of-- people began to walk out-- men, and sometimes women, and then some families, I think all on the same day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think that sort of leadership of-- of the Bund that was-- decided to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so my father went, and my own mother went with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think he maybe thought that he needed her, because he was better known, perhaps as a protection.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we were, I and my sister, and this Polish young woman called Hella were taken to this household of my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we stayed partly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were left partly with the grandparents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother's, yes, who lived-- who-- and my aunt and my sister, my mother's, who had two sons. sons.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother and father left, and we were left on our own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- and then there was-- in fact, Warsaw did become defended.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They somehow changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And was bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the bombs, and the fires, and people putting out the fires with sand and water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when when the Germans came in, I and my sister went to these other grandparents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To stay with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my mother came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She smuggled her-- because by that time the Russians-- you know, there was a pact between Germans and Russians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German-- the Russians came in into Poland and found all these Poles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all these people were hoping to form an army against [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Warsaw. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father-- because somehow got to Vilna, which was then somewhat more independent than Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother then somehow smuggled herself through the Russians and the German front and came back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While you were with your father's parents?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
